Package ie.gmit.sw.wordcloud.main

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColourFactory
    ColourFactory.java - a class that generates and returns an object of type Colour
    ImageGenerator
    ImageGenerator.java - a class that generates the image from a file or URL.
    PositionGenerator
    PositionGenerator.java - a class that generates and returns a random number between 100 and user's max range requested
    WordCloud
    WordCloud.java - a class thats responsible for configuring the word cloud image before any words are rendered on the image
    WordConfig
    WordConfig.java - a class thats responsible for storing the configuration of words that have been parsed
